  "texts": [
    "This study aims to close these research gaps as the university policy on Generative AI acts as a catalyst for institutional and pedagogical changes to ensure ChatGPT is used ethically and responsibly in teaching and learning [56].This research was conducted in a context in which universities are under an urgent need to navigate how to respond to the emergence of ChatGPT and other generative AI technologies.",
    "This case study reviews the approaches adopted by different public universities in Hong Kong, presenting their individual efforts to transition to the changes of a new teaching and learning era.",
    "In the middle of this transition, the authors see the importance to learn through trial and error, so that universities can gain insight that facilitates policy-making and management.",
    "This study addresses the following research questions.1.",
    "What policy and management have the eight public universities in Hong Kongfoot_0 have done since the emergence of ChatGPT? 2."
  ]
}